<div class="heading resPageHeading">


























<h1 >Public Realm</h1></div>

<div class="content stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="f41ed459-0232-4221-9763-ff5f01b11b52" >

    <p>As Ryerson grows, we must continue to provide an engaging network of public spaces that promote a vibrant, welcoming, inspiring and harmonious campus life for our students, employees and the broader community.</p> 
<p>The vision and framework for meeting that goal is outlined in the&nbsp;<strong><a href="/content/dam/facilities-management-development/campus-design-construction/docs/campus-public-realm-plan.pdf"><span class="sr-only">PDF file</span>Ryerson University Campus Public Realm Plan<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-file-pdf-o"></span></a>.</strong>&nbsp;This document provides the vision for Ryerson as a leading innovation university and city builder, and serves as a resource of tools to implement that vision.&nbsp;It sets out flexible guidelines for improving our public spaces that prioritize safety, accessibility and quality of place; and supports our Master Plan Principles, including priorities such as pedestrianization, design excellence and taking a&nbsp;<a href="/hr/work-life/people-first-survey/">People First</a>&nbsp;approach.</p>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#f41ed459-0232-4221-9763-ff5f01b11b52");});</script></div>

				

				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="eac4489b-cde7-493f-8d33-931c4503b6fd" >

    <h2>Frequently asked questions</h2> 
<p>Find out more about the Ryerson University Campus Public Realm Plan, including current and future plans to implement its proposed projects.</p>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#eac4489b-cde7-493f-8d33-931c4503b6fd");});</script></div>

				

				
