                        <a id="accordion-1519232810485-what-is-the-campus-public-realm-plan-" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#" href="#accordion-content-1519232810485-what-is-the-campus-public-realm-plan-" aria-controls="accordion-content-1519232810485-what-is-the-campus-public-realm-plan-" aria-expanded="false">
                            What is the Campus Public Realm Plan?
                        </a>
                    </h3>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1519232810485-what-is-the-campus-public-realm-plan-" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1519232810485-what-is-the-campus-public-realm-plan-">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1519232810485 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="f148172c-08e1-44f9-9e13-087c98eedaf2" >

    <p>The Campus Public Realm plan provides a high level vision, direction and key performance indicators (KPIs) for the development of public realm features on campus.</p>
    





</div>
