<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="1832b838-49a1-447f-9691-c7590a8d0be3" >

    <p>Improvements are planned along Victoria Street and Nelson Mandela Walk from Dundas Street East to Gerrard Street, and on Gould Street from O’Keefe Lane to Bond Street. Visit the <a href="/content/ryerson/facilities-management-development/campus-development/campus-core-revitalization.html">Campus Core Revitalization 2019 project page</a> for more details.</p>
    





