                            What are the major changes planned?
                        </a>
                    </h3>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1519232813983-what-are-the-major-changes-planned-" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1519232813983-what-are-the-major-changes-planned-">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1519232813983 stackparsys">










				
